Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,----------ED01「Twinkle Starlight」----------
Comment: 0,0:18:55.16,0:18:58.65,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,見上げた空高く
Comment: 0,0:18:59.10,0:19:02.06,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,降り注ぐきらめきよ
Comment: 0,0:19:02.33,0:19:04.27,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,Twinkle，Brilliant，
Comment: 0,0:19:04.67,0:19:07.01,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,Wonder Starlight.
Comment: 0,0:19:08.62,0:19:14.00,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,このまま　そっと目蓋とじても
Comment: 0,0:19:17.23,0:19:22.80,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,胸にきらり　輝くよ
Comment: 0,0:19:24.66,0:19:28.29,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,たとえばそうこんな雨の日
Comment: 0,0:19:28.62,0:19:31.87,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,雲間から覗く空に
Comment: 0,0:19:32.11,0:19:38.55,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,明日ヘの願いを込めて
Comment: 0,0:19:38.85,0:19:43.05,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,きっとそこにあるよ（Eternal Starlight）
Comment: 0,0:19:43.05,0:19:46.77,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,導くひかりを（Beyond The Night）
Comment: 0,0:19:46.77,0:19:50.51,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,追いかけ続ける（Over The Blue Sky）
Comment: 0,0:19:50.51,0:19:57.25,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,幼い日のような澄んだ瞳で
Comment: 0,0:19:57.44,0:19:58.24,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,だから
Comment: 0,0:19:58.63,0:20:01.97,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,無窮にまたたく星よ
Comment: 0,0:20:02.32,0:20:05.41,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,希望の祈りたちよ
Comment: 0,0:20:05.61,0:20:12.37,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,想いのせ　銀河の果てまでも
Comment: 0,0:20:12.82,0:20:16.15,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,Twinkle，Twinkle，Twinkle，Twinkle Star.
Comment: 0,0:20:16.15,0:20:20.44,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,Shiny，Bright In The Sky.
Comment: 0,0:20:20.44,0:20:22.13,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,Oh...
Comment: 0,0:20:22.59,0:20:28.00,EDJP,,0,0,0,karaoke,Wonderful Twinkle Starlight.
Comment: 0,0:18:55.16,0:18:58.65,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,抬头仰望无垠夜空
Comment: 0,0:18:59.10,0:19:02.06,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,无数星辰悄然洒落
Comment: 0,0:19:02.33,0:19:04.27,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,闪烁之间
Comment: 0,0:19:04.67,0:19:07.01,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,漫天璀璨
Comment: 0,0:19:08.62,0:19:14.00,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,即使轻轻地闭上双眼
Comment: 0,0:19:17.23,0:19:22.80,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,无尽的光辉犹在心间
Comment: 0,0:19:24.66,0:19:28.29,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,即使整天下雨淅淅沥沥
Comment: 0,0:19:28.62,0:19:31.87,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,也想透过云隙仰望天际
Comment: 0,0:19:32.11,0:19:38.55,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,然后许下明日的恳祈
Comment: 0,0:19:38.85,0:19:43.05,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,它一定就在那{\fnFOT-Chiaro Std B}里{\fn}（永恒星光）
Comment: 0,0:19:43.05,0:19:46.77,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,那指引我的绚丽（划过黑夜）
Comment: 0,0:19:46.77,0:19:50.51,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,我会不住地寻觅（踏上碧空）
Comment: 0,0:19:50.51,0:19:57.25,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,因为眼瞳依旧像儿时那般清晰
Comment: 0,0:19:57.44,0:19:58.24,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,所以啊
Comment: 0,0:19:58.63,0:20:01.97,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,无数闪烁的星辰啊
Comment: 0,0:20:02.32,0:20:05.41,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,无数希望的祈愿啊
Comment: 0,0:20:05.61,0:20:12.37,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,带着我的思念　飞向银河的尽头吧
Comment: 0,0:20:12.82,0:20:16.15,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,闪烁明亮的星辰啊
Comment: 0,0:20:16.15,0:20:20.44,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,放射光明在天际啊
Comment: 0,0:20:20.44,0:20:22.13,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,哇~
Comment: 0,0:20:22.59,0:20:28.00,EDCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,闪烁星光洒满天
